GET /products - List Products with Filtering & Pagination 
Query Parameters: 
{ 
 page?: number; // Page number (default: 1) 
 limit?: number; // Items per page (default: 20, max: 100) 
 search?: string; // Search in product name and SKU 
 category?: string; // Filter by category 
 status?: 'active' | 'inactive' | 'out_of_stock'; // Filter by status 
 supplierId?: string; // Filter by supplier 
 inStock?: boolean; // Filter products in stock 
 sort?: 'Name' | 'SKU' | 'Price' | 'Stock' | 'CreatedAt' | 'UpdatedAt'; // Sort field 
 order?: 'asc' | 'desc'; // Sort order 
}

Response Format: 
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
 data: BackendProduct[]; 
 pagination?: { 
 page: number; 
 limit: number; 
 total: number; 
 pages: number; 
 }; 
}

GET /products/{id} - Get Single Product 
Response Format: 
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
 data: BackendProduct; 
}
POST /products - Create Product 
Request Body: 
{ 
 Name: string; // Required 
 SKU: string; // Required, unique 
 Category: string; // Required 
 Price: number; // Required, >= 0 
 Stock: number; // Required, >= 0 
 MinimumStock: number; // Required, >= 0 
 Status: 'active' | 'inactive' | 'out_of_stock'; // Required 
 Description?: string; // Optional 
 SupplierId: string; // Required 
 Attributes?: BackendProductAttribute[]; // Optional 
 Variants?: BackendProductVariant[]; // Optional 
}
Response Format: 
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
 data: BackendProduct; 
}
PUT /products/{id} - Update Product 

Request Body: Same as POST but all fields optional except those being updated 

Response Format: 
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
 data: BackendProduct; 
}

DELETE /products/{id} - Delete Product 
Response:
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
}

PUT /products/{id}/status - Update Product Status 
Request Body: 
{ 
 status: 'active' | 'inactive' | 'out_of_stock'; 
}

Response Format: 
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
}

POST /products/{id}/images - Upload Product Images 
Request Body: 
FormData with multiple files under 'images' field 
- Max 10 files per upload 
- Max 5MB per file 
- Allowed types: image/jpeg, image/png, image/gif, image/webp
Response Format: 
{ 
 success: boolean; 
 message: string; 
 imageUrls: string[]; // Array of uploaded image URLs 
}
BackendProduct Interface : 
interface BackendProduct { 
 id: string; // UUID 
 Name: string; // Product name 
 SKU: string; // Stock Keeping Unit (unique) 
 Category: string; // Product category 
 Price: number; // Product price 
 Stock: number; // Current stock quantity 
 MinimumStock: number; // Minimum stock threshold 
 Status: 'active' | 'inactive' | 'out_of_stock'; 
 Description?: string; // Product description 
 Image?: string; // Primary image URL 
 Images?: string[]; // All image URLs 
 SupplierId: string; // Associated supplier ID 
 Attributes?: BackendProductAttribute[]; 
 Variants?: BackendProductVariant[]; 
 CreatedAt: string; // ISO 8601 timestamp 
 UpdatedAt: string; // ISO 8601 timestamp 
}
BackendProductAttribute Interface:
interface BackendProductAttribute { 
 Id: string; // Attribute ID 
 Name: string; // Attribute name (e.g., "Brand", "Weight") 
 Value: string; // Attribute value (e.g., "AudioTech", "250g") 
 Type: 'text' | 'number' | 'boolean' | 'select'; 
 Unit?: string; // Optional unit (e.g., "grams", "cm") 
}
BackendProductVariant Interface :
 interface BackendProductVariant { 
 Id: string; // Variant ID 
 Name: string; // Variant name (e.g., "Black", "Large") 
 SKU: string; // Variant SKU 
 Price: number; // Variant price 
 Stock: number; // Variant stock 
 Attributes: Record<string, string>; // Key-value pairs (e.g., {"color": "black", "size": "large"}) 
 Image?: string; // Variant-specific image URL 
}
7. Error Response Format 
All endpoints should return consistent error responses: 
{ 
 success: false; 
 message: string; // Human-readable error message 
 error?: string; // Error code or type 
 errors?: string[]; // Array of validation errors 
}
