- `ID`: Int (Primary Key, auto-increment)
- `Name`: String? (optional, NVarChar(Max))
- `Description`: String? (optional, NVarChar(Max))
- `Price`: Decimal (required, Decimal(18,2))
- `Stock`: Int? (optional)
