- `Images[]` (one-to-many)
- `ProductAttribute[]` (one-to-many)
- `ProductVariant[]` (one-to-many)
- `Categories` (many-to-one, required)
- `Suppliers?` (many-to-one, optional)
- `Customer?` (many-to-one, optional)
- `OrderItem[]`, `CartItem[]`, `Reviews[]`, `WishlistItem[]`

