 1	# Customer Management API Documentation
 2	
 3	## Overview
 4	The Customer Management API provides comprehensive endpoints for managing customers in the ConnectChain Admin Panel. All endpoints require JWT Bearer Token authentication.
 5	
 6	## Base URL
 7	```
 8	/api/users
 9	```
 10	
 11	## Authentication
 12	All endpoints require a valid JWT Bearer Token in the Authorization header:
 13	```
 14	Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
 15	```
