 222	
 223	### 6. Upload Product Images
 224	**POST** `/api/products/:id/images`
 225	
 226	Upload multiple images for a product (max 10 files, 5MB each).
 227	
 228	**Parameters:**
 229	- `id` (number, required): Product ID
 230	
 231	**Request Body:**
 232	- Form data with `images` field containing multiple image files
 233	- Supported formats: jpg, jpeg, png, gif, webp
 234	
 235	**Response:**
 236	```json
 237	{
 238	 "success": true,
 239	 "message": "Images uploaded successfully",
 240	 "imageUrls": [
 241	 "https://cloudinary.com/image1.jpg",
 242	 "https://cloudinary.com/image2.jpg"
 243	 ]
 244	}
 245	```
 246	
 247	## Error Responses
 248	
 249	All endpoints return consistent error responses:
 250	
 251	```json
 252	{
 253	 "success": false,
 254	 "message": "Error description"
 255	}
...
 268	
 269	**Products Table:**
 270	- `ID` (int, auto-increment, primary key)
 271	- `Name` (string, optional)
 272	- `Description` (string, optional)
 273	- `Price` (decimal, required)
 274	- `Stock` (int, optional)
 275	- `MinimumStock` (int, default: 0)
 276	- `SKU` (UniqueIdentifier, auto-generated)
 277	- `CategoryId` (int, required, foreign key)
 278	- `SupplierId` (string, optional, foreign key)
 279	- `CustomerId` (string, optional, foreign key)
 280	- `Deleted` (boolean)
 281	- `CreatedDate` (DateTime)
 282	- `UpdatedDate` (DateTime, optional)
 283	
 284	**Related Tables:**
 285	- `Images` - Product images
 286	- `ProductAttribute` - Key-value attributes
 287	- `ProductVariant` - Product variants with custom pricing
 288	- `Categories` - Product categories
 289	- `Suppliers` - Product suppliers
 290	- `Customer` - Associated customers
 291	- `Reviews` - Product reviews
 292	
 293	## File Structure
 294	```
 295	src/modules/Products/
 296	 products.controller.js # Request handlers and response mapping
 297	 products.service.js # Business logic and database operations
 298	 products.routes.js # Route definitions and middleware
 299	 products.validation.js # Joi validation schemas
 300	 README.md # This documentation
 301	```
