## **Frontend Request Format**

### **HTTP Method & URL:**
```
DELETE /api/products/:productId/images/:imageId
```

### **Required Parameters (URL Path):**
- **`productId`** (integer): The ID of the product that owns the image
- **`imageId`** (integer): The ID of the specific image to delete

### **Required Headers:**
```javascript
{
 "Authorization": "Bearer your-jwt-token",
 "Content-Type": "application/json" // Optional for DELETE requests
}
```

### **Request Body:**
```
NO BODY REQUIRED - This is a DELETE request with parameters in the URL only
```

