 16	
 17	### GET /api/suppliers
 18	Get all suppliers with pagination, search, and filtering.
 19	
 20	**Query Parameters:**
 21	- `page` (optional): Page number (default: 1)
 22	- `limit` (optional): Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)
 23	- `search` (optional): Search in supplier name and email
 24	- `verificationStatus` (optional): Filter by verification status (`verified`, `pending`)
 25	- `status` (optional): Filter by supplier status (`active`, `banned`)
 26	- `sort` (optional): Sort field (`Name`, `Email`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`)
 27	- `order` (optional): Sort order (`asc`, `desc`)
 28	
 29	### GET /api/suppliers/:id
 30	Get detailed information about a specific supplier.
 31	
 32	### GET /api/suppliers/:id/products
 33	Get all products belonging to a specific supplier with pagination.
...
 81	
 82	### Field Mappings
 83	| API Field | Database Field | Description |
 84	|-----------|----------------|-------------|
 85	| `id` | `Suppliers.Id` | Unique identifier (GUID) |
 86	| `name` | `Users.Name` | Contact person name |
 87	| `email` | `Users.Email` | Supplier email address |
 88	| `phone` | `Users.PhoneNumber` | Supplier phone number |
 89	| `address` | `Users.Address` | Supplier address |
 90	| `contactPerson` | `Users.Name` | Contact person name (same as name) |
 91	| `logo` | `Users.ImageUrl` | Supplier logo URL |
 92	| `status` | `Users.LockoutEnabled` | Account status (active/banned) |
 93	| `verificationStatus` | `Users.EmailConfirmed` | Email verification status |
 94	| `categories` | `Users.BusinessType` | Supplier business type/category |
...
