 486	## Implementation Notes
 487	
 488	### Schema Compliance
 489	 **All field names match the Prisma schema exactly:**
 490	- Uses `Users.Id` for supplier identification
 491	- Maps `contactPerson` to `Users.Name` field
 492	- Uses `Users.LockoutEnabled` for status management
 493	- Uses `Users.EmailConfirmed` for verification status
 494	- Single category support via `Users.BusinessType` field
 495	
 496	### Security Features
 497	- JWT token authentication required for all endpoints
 498	- Password hashing using ASP.NET Core Identity compatible hasher
 499	- Account lockout management
 500	- Email verification workflow
...
