 91	| `logo` | `Users.ImageUrl` | Supplier logo URL |
 92	| `status` | `Users.LockoutEnabled` | Account status (active/banned) |
 93	| `verificationStatus` | `Users.EmailConfirmed` | Email verification status |
 94	| `categories` | `Users.BusinessType` | Supplier business type/category |
