 124	
 125	### 3. Create Product
 126	**POST** `/api/products`
 127	
 128	Create a new product with optional attributes and variants.
 129	
 130	**Request Body:**
 131	```json
 132	{
 133	 "Name": "New Product",
 134	 "Description": "Product description",
 135	 "Price": 99.99,
 136	 "Stock": 100,
 137	 "MinimumStock": 10,
 138	 "CategoryId": 1,
 139	 "SupplierId": "supplier-guid",
 140	 "CustomerId": "customer-guid",
 141	 "Attributes": [
 142	 {
 143	 "Key": "Brand",
 144	 "Value": "Samsung"
 145	 },
 146	 {
 147	 "Key": "Color",
 148	 "Value": "Black"
 149	 }
 150	 ],
 151	 "Variants": [
 152	 {
 153	 "Name": "Small",
 154	 "Type": "Size",
 155	 "CustomPrice": 89.99,
 156	 "Stock": 50
 157	 },
 158	 {
 159	 "Name": "Large",
 160	 "Type": "Size",
 161	 "CustomPrice": 109.99,
 162	 "Stock": 30
 163	 }
 164	 ]
 165	}
 166	```
 167	
 168	**Response:**
 169	```json
 170	{
 171	 "success": true,
 172	 "message": "Product created successfully",
 173	 "data": {
 174	 // Product object with generated ID and SKU
 175	 }
 176	}
...
 268	
 269	**Products Table:**
 270	- `ID` (int, auto-increment, primary key)
 271	- `Name` (string, optional)
 272	- `Description` (string, optional)
 273	- `Price` (decimal, required)
 274	- `Stock` (int, optional)
 275	- `MinimumStock` (int, default: 0)
 276	- `SKU` (UniqueIdentifier, auto-generated)
 277	- `CategoryId` (int, required, foreign key)
 278	- `SupplierId` (string, optional, foreign key)
 279	- `CustomerId` (string, optional, foreign key)
 280	- `Deleted` (boolean)
 281	- `CreatedDate` (DateTime)
 282	- `UpdatedDate` (DateTime, optional)
 283	
 284	**Related Tables:**
 285	- `Images` - Product images
 286	- `ProductAttribute` - Key-value attributes
 287	- `ProductVariant` - Product variants with custom pricing
 288	- `Categories` - Product categories
 289	- `Suppliers` - Product suppliers
 290	- `Customer` - Associated customers
 291	- `Reviews` - Product reviews
 292	
