 81	
 82	### Field Mappings
 83	| API Field | Database Field | Description |
 84	|-----------|----------------|-------------|
 85	| `id` | `Suppliers.Id` | Unique identifier (GUID) |
 86	| `name` | `Users.Name` | Contact person name |
 87	| `email` | `Users.Email` | Supplier email address |
 88	| `phone` | `Users.PhoneNumber` | Supplier phone number |
 89	| `address` | `Users.Address` | Supplier address |
 90	| `contactPerson` | `Users.Name` | Contact person name (same as name) |
 91	| `logo` | `Users.ImageUrl` | Supplier logo URL |
 92	| `status` | `Users.LockoutEnabled` | Account status (active/banned) |
 93	| `verificationStatus` | `Users.EmailConfirmed` | Email verification status |
 94	| `categories` | `Users.BusinessType` | Supplier business type/category |
 95	
 96	### Status Management
 97	- **Active**: `LockoutEnabled = false`
 98	- **Banned**: `LockoutEnabled = true`
 99	- **Verified**: `EmailConfirmed = true`
 100	- **Pending**: `EmailConfirmed = false`
 101	
 102	### Relationships
 103	```
 104	Users (1) (1) Suppliers
 105	Suppliers (1) (*) Products
 106	Products (1) (*) ProductVariant
 107	Products (1) (*) ProductAttribute
 108	Products (1) (*) Images
 109	Products (1) (1) Categories
 110	```
